<li> <em><a href="http://groups.yahoo.com/group/activatedaudience">The Laugh and Learn Ledger (The Importance of the Arts article)</a></em></li>
<li> <em><a href="http://www.ustream.tv/channel/activated-storytellers-live">Act!vated Ustream</a> - Watch August 12th.</em></li>
</ul>]]></description>
